<div class="panel-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-node"   class="panel-pane pane-node">
  
        <h2 class="pane-title">Admission</h2>
    
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <article class="node node-page node-published node-not-promoted node-not-sticky author-admin odd clearfix" id="node-page-7">
            
  
  <div class="content clearfix">
    <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><h6>Admission Rates</h6>
<table><tbody><tr><td>Adults</td>
<td>$10.00</td>
</tr><tr><td>Seniors (65 and older)</td>
<td>$8.00</td>
</tr><tr><td>Students (ages 13-22)</td>
<td>$8.00</td>
</tr><tr><td>Children (ages 6-12)</td>
<td>$4.00</td>
</tr><tr><td>Children (ages 5 &amp; under)</td>
<td>FREE</td>
</tr><tr><td>Purchase an All-Day Family* Pass</td>
<td>$30.00</td>
</tr><tr><td>Annual Individual Membership**<br />
(Season-long admission)</td>
<td>$40.00</td>
</tr><tr><td>Annual Family* Membership**<br />
Season-long admission)</td>
<td>$80.00</td>
</tr><tr><td>Lifetime</td>
<td>$500.00</td>
</tr></tbody></table><p>*Family is defined as parents and their children under 18.<br />
**Membership entitles you to vote at our annual general meeting, and gives you FREE or reduced admission to FIVE other Signature Museums in Manitoba:</p>
<ul><li>Commonwealth Air Training Plan Museum — Brandon,</li>
<li>Manitoba Agricultural Museum — Austin,</li>
<li>New Iceland Heritage Museum — Gimli,</li>
<li>St. Boniface Museum — Winnipeg,</li>
<li>Western Canada Aviation Museum — Winnipeg.</li>
</ul></div></div></div>  </div>
  
