      <div class="inside"><div class="panel-pane pane-custom pane-1"   class="panel-pane pane-custom pane-1">
  
      
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <p class="centered" style="margin-top:20px; margin-bottom:20px"><a href="/events" class="grey button" rel="nofollow">Calendar of Events</a></p>
<div class="box-highlight">Visitors are welcome to enjoy a self-guided tour.<br />
Please allow 1½ to 2 hours to benefit from the full experience.</div>
<p>On event days, and on certain other days when they have been arranged in advance, Horse-drawn Wagon Rides are available on the village grounds. (Rides can be prearranged for special occasions, groups or tours)</p>
<p>We encourage people to enjoy their experience with us but to work with us to assure safety and the preservation of our museum. We ask you to refrain from smoking except in designated areas and to work with us in matters of safety.</p>
